In the field of coastal and maritime tourism, EUCC is member of ECOTRANS and DestiNet. Together we have working relationships with DG GROW.&#xd;
&#xd;
EUCC is member of the ECNC Group, consisting of Coastal &amp; Marine Union – EUCC, and the EUCC MedCentre. The Group offers an additional network to facilitate access to European institutions.&#xd;
	&#xd;
EUCC is a founding member of the European Habitats Forum (EHF), a coalition of NGOs advising DG Environment on habitats and Natura 2000 issues.
